value.0: The stench of decay permeates the area around this being. Ancient tattered robes, and tarnished jewelry speak to the age of this particular lich. To the sharp of eye, and avid historians, the signet ring he wears bears the crest of house Bathrie.
This item is not for PC use. If you have somehow come into possession of this, please contact a DM to have it removed and do not use it.

Value.value: As soon as you descend the stairs, a magical barrier phases into existence behind you, trapping you inside.
*You step on a shard of bone, releasing harmful necromantic energy*
